text: The Seventh Continent () is a 1966 Croatian Czech fantasy movie directed by Dušan Vukotić and starring Demeter Bitenc, Vanja Drach, Oudy Rachmat Endang, Mikloš Huba, Karla Chadimová, Viktor Starčić, Iris Vrus. ==Other websites== * Category:1966 fantasy movies Category:Croatian movies Category:Czech fantasy movies Category:Movies set on islands
title: The Seventh Continent (1966 movie)
